{"tid":1163340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[MAGA]  美國與澳洲Lynas簽署合作協議 防中國阻斷出口稀土","createTime":"2019-05-20T11:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T00:28:57.000Z","uid":141151,"like":70,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"678457960bce0757b8e279b85f2c08b96e50d5a6","tid":1163340,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:40:41.000Z","msg":"美國與澳洲Lynas簽署合作協議 防中國阻斷出口稀土<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2796094\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2796094&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=69770e64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2796094&h=cbeebba2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2796094</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美中貿易戰近期再升級，兩國擴大關稅清單規模，不過對美國極為重要的原料稀土，至今仍未涉入貿易戰中。而今美國未雨綢繆先找出路，為了預防中國停止出口稀土報復，已經和澳洲出產稀土的Lynas簽署合作備忘錄。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">本次澳洲Lynas是與美國德州的Blue Line集團簽署合作協議，幫助美國在本土建立1座稀土分離工廠。澳洲Lynas是目前除了中國外，最大的稀土公司，同時擁有分離、提取、蒐集等專業知識，這回合作剛好可以補上美國最缺乏的分離技術。<br />\n<br />\n而在美國Blue Line集團與澳洲Lynas合作後，將可以解決美國稀土關鍵的供應鏈問題，屆時一旦中國阻斷出口稀土到美國，傷害也將降到最低。根據統計，目前美國約有80%的稀土是和中國進口。</span><br />\n<br />\n稀土是電動車、電子裝置等產品的零件原料，特別是在汽車逐漸轉變為電動車的時候，美國民眾對電動車需求也越來越大，讓稀土供應量更顯得重要。"},{"pid":"79b35274d0ef8bfae3278ef2dc93f4c2c747a9ed","tid":1163340,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d515329c51201ef2334185393cdd51e06cbd4c6","tid":1163340,"uid":3704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:47:43.000Z","msg":"贏國又贏"},{"pid":"a0a7bd14e463c2343b234d84dc64f04810c31576","tid":1163340,"uid":29702,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:48:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9057d2e078011204726f005d92eaaf23ad1f0b21","tid":1163340,"uid":31637,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:51:34.000Z","msg":"美國真係好撚癲，連中國之後幾步棋都計算埋"},{"pid":"6748fefbbe9fbfe3c3cb3a48d4b37feb70fa53b0","tid":1163340,"uid":21470,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a0a7bd14e463c2343b234d84dc64f04810c31576","tid":1163340,"uid":29702,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:48:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:54:23.000Z","msg":"都唔快架啦，比左中國一年時間<br />\n依加公佈簽約唔係真係呢幾個月先搞架ma"},{"pid":"729f1944457eca6966a0287f036157ed814aa11e","tid":1163340,"uid":239519,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:58:35.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲：吓，稀土唔係中國獨有既咩 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76041cda851047afe06f1942eda45970561812e","tid":1163340,"uid":48083,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T12:14:12.000Z","msg":"大意：<br />\n1. 美國同日本都有相當多既儲備同礦<br />\n2. 稀土工業應用專利喺美國手上，美國都有出口稀土加工品俾中國<br />\n3. 中國自己都係淨入口國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2019/05/17/chinese-rare-earth-great-advantage/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2019%2F05%2F17%2Fchinese-rare-earth-great-advantage%2F&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=52118f31\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2019/05/17/chinese-rare-earth-great-advantage/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com.tw/n281704/稀土金屬並非中共的籌碼.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com.tw%2Fn281704%2F%E7%A8%80%E5%9C%9F%E9%87%91%E5%B1%AC%E4%B8%A6%E9%9D%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E7%9A%84%E7%B1%8C%E7%A2%BC.html&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2